  ('dietitian-moex-09737', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-096-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '有一酵素在受質濃度0.01 M時，催化反應速率是20μmol/min，此酵素對受質的K 值是1×10 M。此酵 m 素遵守Michaelis-Menten動力學，當受質濃度為10-6 M時，其反應速率是：', '["1.8μmol/min", "18μmol/min", "10μmol/min", "無法計算"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:54+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a5e1ee9083b2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d1518fd8ddee", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "096130", "c": "113", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "096", "exam_name": "096年第二次專技高普考醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、營養師、獸醫佐、醫師分試考試", "original_question_number": 29, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-09738', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-096-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '查格夫法則（Chargaff''s rules）敘述的是在DNA分子中：', '["A＝G", "A＝U", "A＋G＝T＋C", "A＋T＝G＋C"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:54+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a5e1ee9083b2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d1518fd8ddee", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "096130", "c": "113", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "096", "exam_name": "096年第二次專技高普考醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、營養師、獸醫佐、醫師分試考試", "original_question_number": 30, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-09739', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-096-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '當雙股DNA在中性pH下加熱，下列何種變化不會發生？', '["UV 260 nm吸光值增加", "在氮鹼基與五碳醣間的糖苷鍵被打斷", "雙股螺旋鬆開", "氮鹼基間的氫鍵被破壞"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:54+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a5e1ee9083b2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d1518fd8ddee", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "096130", "c": "113", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "096", "exam_name": "096年第二次專技高普考醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、營養師、獸醫佐、醫師分試考試", "original_question_number": 31, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
