  ('dietitian-moex-09741', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-096-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '五碳醣磷酸鹽途徑（the pentose phosphate pathway）主要的功能是：', '["和糖解作用（glycolysis）一樣是提供能量的主要代謝途徑", "提供五碳醣和NADPH", "提供五碳醣和ATP", "利用胺基酸的碳骨架合成醣類"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:54+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a5e1ee9083b2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d1518fd8ddee", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "096130", "c": "113", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "096", "exam_name": "096年第二次專技高普考醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、營養師、獸醫佐、醫師分試考試", "original_question_number": 33, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-09742', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-096-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '胞嘧啶（Cytosine）和尿嘧啶（uracil）分解代謝會產生一種獨特的胺基酸是：', '["β-丙胺酸（β-alanine）", "β-胺基丁酸（β-amino-butyrate）", "尿酸（uric acid）", "牛磺酸（taurine）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:54+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a5e1ee9083b2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d1518fd8ddee", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "096130", "c": "113", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "096", "exam_name": "096年第二次專技高普考醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、營養師、獸醫佐、醫師分試考試", "original_question_number": 34, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-09743', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-096-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '在檸檬酸循環（citric acid cycle）中，中間代謝物的順序是：', '["檸檬酸（citrate）→異檸檬酸（isocitrate）→α酮戊二酸（α-ketoglutarate）→琥珀酸（succinate）→蘋果酸 （malate）→延胡索酸（fumarate）→丁酮二酸（oxaloacetate）", "異檸檬酸→檸檬酸→α酮戊二酸→琥珀酸→延胡索酸→蘋果酸→丁酮二酸", "檸檬酸→異檸檬酸→α酮戊二酸→琥珀酸→延胡索酸→蘋果酸→丁酮二酸", "異檸檬酸→檸檬酸→α酮戊二酸→延胡索酸→琥珀酸→蘋果酸→丁酮二酸"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:54+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a5e1ee9083b2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d1518fd8ddee", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "096130", "c": "113", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "096", "exam_name": "096年第二次專技高普考醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、營養師、獸醫佐、醫師分試考試", "original_question_number": 35, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL)
